中等師資培育課程基本能力指標 Basic Ability Index





編號Code
指標名稱Basic Ability Index
本科目對應之指標Correspondent Index
達成該項基本能力之考評方式Methods Of Evaluating This Ability

1能掌握學科知識、學科教學知識以及學生發展與學習知識Able to have a full grasp of pedagogical content knowledge of subject matter as well as student development and prerequisite knowledge in the subject matter.●》出缺席狀況》課堂討論與表現》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)》作業成績》展演》資料蒐集與分析》團隊參與》學習綜合表現》其他(模擬試教)2能依據課程目標與學生特性規劃課程和設計教學活動Able to plan lessons and design teaching activities according to teaching objectives and student characteristics.●》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)》作業成績》實作(含分組演練/合作等)》學習綜合表現》其他(模擬試教)3能運用適當的教學策略與資源Able to apply appropriate teaching strategies and resources.●》課堂討論與表現》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)》作業成績》學習綜合表現》其他(模擬試教)4能評量學生學習情形並據以調整教學Able to evaluate student learning and make necessary changes in teaching accordingly .●》課堂討論與表現》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)5能提升學生的學習成效Able to enhance effective learning for students.●》出缺席狀況》課堂討論與表現》報告(含個人或小組、口頭或書面、專題、訪問、觀察等形式)》實作(含分組演練/合作等)》其他(模擬試教)6能營造有助於學習的環境Able to create helpful learning environment.&nbsp&nbsp7能妥善運用資源對學生進行輔導Able to appropriately utilize available resources for the services of student counseling and consultation  .&nbsp&nbsp8能致力於反思與專業成長Able to devote him/herself to reflections on improving teaching as well as professional growth .&nbsp&nbsp9能與服務學校建立正向的互動關係Able to build positive and interactive relations with schools where he/she works.&nbsp&nbsp10能善盡教育專業責任Able to take responsibilities in the profession of education.&nbsp&nbsp

			



二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required Texts
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources1. Van Tassel-Baska, Joyce, Johnson, Dana T., and Boyce, Linda Neal. 1996. Developing Verbal Talent: Ideas and Strategies for Teachers of Elementary and Middle School Students. London: Allyn and Bacon.2. Brown, H. D. (2007). Teaching by principles: An interactive approach to language pedagogy (3rd ed.). White Plains, New York: Longman.3. Bowman-Kruhm, M. (2006). Whole language: What it is, what it isn’t. Retrieved August 5,2006, from http://www.spelling.org/Essays/whole_language.htm4. Savignon, S. J. (1997). Shaping the curriculum (Chapter 5). In S. J. Savignon, Communicative competence: Theory and classroom practice (2nd ed.) (pp. 169-208). Sydney: McGraw-Hills.5.施玉惠 (民90)。讀寫教學與評量。教育部國民中小學英語教學及評量模式研究報告。6. 教師印發之講義或學習活動單


三、教學目標 Objectives


1. 瞭解任教科目適用的教學模式,重要教學法及目前國高中推行的的教學方法，以期能熟習任教科目的教學活動。 2. 練習任教科目單元教學活動設計，以期能掌握單元教學的流程與要點。 3. 透過單元教學活動之演練，以期能整合應用所學，奠定未來實際進行任教科目課程教學的知能，以及參加教   師甄試的信心。1. To explore the suitable teaching styles, the important teaching approaches and the on-going teaching methods applied in junior and senior high schools nowadays.2. To design and practice the teaching plans and to foster students to seize the key points when teaching. 3. To organize what students have learned and apply them into the micro-teaching, and then to  build up students’ confidence in teaching. 


 


