六、隨筆


 
﻿
生活隨筆
We should spend more time on those students who are not good at English by teaching them to read picture story book.  Once the students are interested in learning English, they will have a better chance to love English.  English should not be taught as a language and a subject for exams in elementary school.  English is a tool for us to learn more.  Please don't ask our students to memorize vocabulary when they are the first or second graders.  Vocabulary should be acquired in a meaning context, such as an interesting story.


七、專長授課


 
1.閱讀與寫作
2.英文補救教學


